<title>USA: Parcplace announces restructuring.</title>
<headline>Parcplace announces restructuring.</headline>
<dateline>SUNNYVALE, Calif. 1997-07-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>ParcPlace-Digitalk Inc said Monday it began reducing its U.S. operations and &quot;refocusing its strategic vision.&quot;</p>
<p>&quot;We will continue to reevaluate our world-wide operations and will adjust accordingly in an effort to bring ParcPlace back to a level of profitability,&quot; chief financial officer Ronald Clear said in the statment.</p>
<p>According to the statement the company is reducing operational costs to be more in line with its new projected revenues.</p>
<p>The company said it would report first quarter earnings on August 7.</p>
<p>No further details were given and no one was immediately available for comment.</p>
